{"tid":1404585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"數據講野：目標應以keep住public opinion為先, 提醒手足應退則退","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:18:05.000Z","uid":295985,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2497ec45cd37ce616fd6b8a4201c5153e1ede537","tid":1404585,"uid":295985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/report/antiextraditionbillfreq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Freport%2Fantiextraditionbillfreq&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USOisLzr3S4L08%2B1QJ77HZeU%3D&h=83778cca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/report/antiextraditionbillfreq</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民調中心報告：數據分析<br />\n<br />\n睇sampling method屬於random sampling同小心地列出問既方法，客觀事實指出研究結果係有代表性既，由demographic data黎睇，年齡分佈平均。要格硬講50-59歲既比例較其他組別多，但大致可接受。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50avU5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50avU5t.jpg&h=cb539c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個特別注意點，係受訪人64%都無參與過反修例遊行或集會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fe2aU5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFe2aU5B.jpg&h=c6728db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔存在果啲相信「地球係平既」人所講既「做假」。<br />\n<br />\n內容重點：<br />\n五大訴求當中大部分已是港人共識（過半數）我，包括：設立獨立調查委員會、全面撒回、不將示威定性為暴動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1ydSS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1ydSS8.jpg&h=6aa8eac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港人大多對警察不滿警隊表現評分<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSq0xSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSq0xSU.jpg&h=d42e42c2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但亦認為示威者過激，經常使用過份武力。呢個係市民個係普遍印象黎既，就算人數比例上唔係真，都要留意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqOaaFO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqOaaFO.jpg&h=71a2897c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而問題成因方面，大部份認為係對政權不信任 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iLaco0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiLaco0W.jpg&h=7bfd594f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認真，要有心理準備，unlike由政府方面得到公義。所以等選舉，民意已經夠做！請大家繼續和理非做宣傳同爭取支持。<br />\n<br />\n以keep住public opinion為先, 提醒手足應退則退。<br />\n手足唔好搵命搏！<br />\n[認同請推]"},{"pid":"4eeb565af982a0b40b89c2028c81f8fec94473dd","tid":1404585,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a56b8dbb1646e24924a44f0b4a4d352f92a54e0","tid":1404585,"uid":262035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"個survey 純粹帶出有人覺得示威者行為偏過激<br />\n但無講到啲人支唔支持啲行動<br />\n<br />\n而家個困局就係唔激純和理非個政府就理閪你<br />\n所以一定要擦邊球咁玩"},{"pid":"8aa94623c0447348b0838570b278721ab845eafe","tid":1404585,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7751ed9bcf0cd487485768b2e9304396d94e30ac","tid":1404585,"uid":295985,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3a56b8dbb1646e24924a44f0b4a4d352f92a54e0","tid":1404585,"uid":262035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"個survey 純粹帶出有人覺得示威者行為偏過激<br />\n但無講到啲人支唔支持啲行動<br />\n<br />\n而家個困局就係唔激純和理非個政府就理閪你<br />\n所以一定要擦邊球咁玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:38:44.000Z","msg":"明白不能以完全守法來達義，因係「法治」已被高官警察玩弄。<br />\n<br />\n但公務員類既和理非集會的確會喺市民聽落係有好大回響。所以政府工聯會民建聯警察呀乜呀，呢堆唔關事既人，先會係咁出黎講啲無用既野。《公務員參與罷工的權利》中已表明罷工合情合理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2Ffiles%2Fpanel060314c.pdf&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USOisLzr3S4L08%2B1QJ77HZeU%3D&h=f8acb73e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地最驚我地和平而最有穩定代表性既一群去表達，證明方向正確。全民罷工亦係正確之路。"},{"pid":"09f275de0b9e270157c2c7be3dc7b922a563506e","tid":1404585,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ed53e0cefa13f60cb98e878fbe385fc87752426","tid":1404585,"uid":295985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a56b8dbb1646e24924a44f0b4a4d352f92a54e0","tid":1404585,"uid":262035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"個survey 純粹帶出有人覺得示威者行為偏過激<br />\n但無講到啲人支唔支持啲行動<br />\n<br />\n而家個困局就係唔激純和理非個政府就理閪你<br />\n所以一定要擦邊球咁玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"仲有佢果條有關示威者用既5-point Likert scale, 4分同5分既wording係「過份使用武力」，相信撰得呢兩個option既人，會用「過份」黎描述，應該係唔支持。我一般接受既應該會撰1-3"},{"pid":"af2c5e2f22d4cbe6fa84b50b2f01a47d61f39cd9","tid":1404585,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2817a08f378321decdf56041ecb2befcab0c935b","tid":1404585,"uid":191012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"啲「一半一半」「唔知」「5/10」仲有好多人投<br />\n即喺仲有好多中間派港豬未覺醒<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc8254fd00f62c0f1d0b0a0449ae720adcd56ff","tid":1404585,"uid":295985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2817a08f378321decdf56041ecb2befcab0c935b","tid":1404585,"uid":191012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"啲「一半一半」「唔知」「5/10」仲有好多人投<br />\n即喺仲有好多中間派港豬未覺醒<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"啲警察近來short左係咁烚普通街坊，又打路人，好快會民怨四起，而家18區tear gas bingo陸續有黎<br />\n <br />\nPublic opinion!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}